% Psychtoolbox:PsychFiles.%% help Psychtoolbox % For an overview, triple-click me & hit enter.%%   ChangeStringsHere   - Change strings in all files in a folder (DANGEROUS!).%   CopyFile            - Copy a file.%   DesktopFolder       - Path for Desktop Folder on Matlab disk.%   DiskRoot            - Path for root of Matlab disk.%   FindFolder          - Find a folder on disk.%   FindStringInFile    - Find instances of string in one file.%   FindStringshere     - Find instances of a string all files in a folder.%   GetFilenames        - Get names of files in a folder.%   filetype            - Get/set creator and type of a file (MEX).%   LiteralUnderscore   - Insert escape ("\") before each underscore char in string.%   ReadStructsFromText - Read struct array from a tab delimited text file.%   SaveAsEps           - Save matrix as an EPS file.%   SearchAndReplace    - Change strings in one file (DANGEROUS!).%   QuoteString         - Wrap a string in quotes, double embedded quotes.%   WriteStructsToText  - Write a struct array to a tab delimited text file.%% NOTE: The routines that change strings are buggy. Make a backup first, just in case.% Copyright (c) 1996-2003 by Denis Pelli & David Brainard; % Except for:%   filetype, which is copyright (c) Erik A. Johnson.